		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />The 3DS seems like a reasonable target for a homebrew Virtual Boy emulator. Of course, that assumes that a useful exploit is found.<br /><br />I don't think the Virtual Boy had an option to play the games in 2D, though. Things might look a little weird if you turn off 3D, and the slider won't have any effect on depth.

		

